345
00:18:07,211 --> 00:18:08,295
- à! - [Vợ Won Dae thở dài ngạc nhiên]

346
00:18:09,213 --> 00:18:10,589
Ờ, xin lỗi, xin lỗi.

347
00:18:10,672 --> 00:18:11,882
Đánh chết con khốn này...

348
00:18:13,008 --> 00:18:14,009
